name: Grammy's Mandala
description: This is a special one for me. My Grammy would have been 100 this year. She passed away last January. It's hard to believe its been a year. I used her date of birth to choose the colors and patterns for this one. She was a fiery little Sicilian woman and I miss her dearly. I'm doing 100 editions of this mandala in honor of how old she would be this year. Ti voglio bene e mi manchi tanto nonna <3
